# Lockfile is intentionally excluded — the Dockerfile runs `npm install`
# directly inside the Alpine container so it always resolves packages with
# Docker's own npm/platform, avoiding version-mismatch failures that occur
# when developers run npm install on Windows (npm v11) vs the container (npm v10).
# package-lock.json
